item.title: 2006 in Pictures!
item.description: Well, after going almost 2 weeks with a very nasty cold, I got better just in time for the new year! This has proven to be a rather eventfull year for me and my family, as I travelled and met more new people than in the previous 5 years combined! Since everyone seems to be posting about what they’ve accomplished throught the year 2006, here’s my photographic attempt. January 2006
